

Project Name: SIMPLE CALCULATOR

Description: The "SIMPLE CALCULATOR" is a C++ application developed as part of the Level 1_Task2 assignment during the intern's time at CodSoft. It is a basic calculator that can perform addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division operations. The calculator provides a user-friendly interface for inputting numbers and operators.

Development Environment:

IDE: Visual Studio
Language: C++
Tools: .Net Framework

Key Features:

Addition, Subtraction, Multiplication, and Division operations


